This has been introduced because of the wierd behavior of Informatica - not picking up value of the 1st parameter in parameter file. TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select sum (uq_qty) , model_typ_cd , count(*) from vrap.rcit_base_clm_inv where NRE_CLM_CD = '0' and model_typ_cd = '$$MODEL_TYP_CD' and inv_elig_dt between $$MAX_QTR_STRT_DT and $$MAX_QTR_END_DT GROUP BY MODEL_TYP_CD

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select model_typ_cd , sum(grs_clm_cnt) grs_clm_cnt , sum(dspnsd_qty) dsnpnsd_qty from VRAP.TAPC_QTR_TOTALS where quarter_id = $$MAX_GDX_QUARTER_ID and model_typ_cd = '$$MODEL_TYP_CD' group by model_typ_cd
